net.opentsdb.core

类 FillingDownsampler

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.opentsdb.core.Downsampler
      • net.opentsdb.core.FillingDownsampler
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    Iterator<DataPoint>, DataPoint, SeekableView

    public class FillingDownsampler
extends Downsampler
    A specialized downsampler that returns special values, based on the fill policy, for intervals for which no data could be found. The default implementation, Downsampler, simply skips intervals that have no data, which causes the AggregationIterator up the chain to interpolate.
    从以下版本开始:
    2.2
